can Film Critics Awards|Nafca]]\n|Best Actress Diaspora\n|Turning Point\n|{{won}}<ref>{{Cite web | url=http://ameyawdebrah.com/fab-photos-jackie-appiah-kofi-adjorlologenevieve-nnaji-others-win-nollywood-african-film-critics-awards-washington-dc/ |title = FAB Photos: Jackie Appiah, Kofi Adjorlolo,Genevieve Nnaji, others win at Nollywood & African Film Critics Awards in Washington DC|date = 16 September 2013}}</ref>\n|-\n|Pyprus Magazine Screen Actors Awards\n|Best International Actress\n|\n|{{won}}<ref>[http://www.nigeriamovienetwork.com/articles/read-jackie-appiah-wins-best-international-actress-award-at-pamsaa-2013_789.html]{{dead link|date=March 2020}}</ref>\n|-\n|The F.A.C.E List Awards (USA)\n|Achievement In Africa Entertainment\n|\n|{{won}}<ref>{{Cite web | url=http://blueblood006.blogspot.com/2013/06/jackie-appiah-honoured-for-her.html?m=1 |title = Blueblood's Corner: Jackie Appiah Honoured for Her Excellence in Africa's Entertainment Industry|date = 20 June 2013}}</ref>\n|-\n|rowspan=3|2014\n|[[2014 Africa Magic Viewers Choice Awards]]\n|Best Actress Comedy Role\n|Cheaters\n|{{nominated}}\n|-\n|rowspan=2|[[2014 Ghana Movie Awards]]\n|Best Actress Leading Role\n|rowspan=2|Sisters At War\n|{{nominated}}\n|-\n|Favorite Actress\n|{{nominated}}\n|-\n|rowspan=2|2015\n|[[2015 Africa Magic Viewers Choice Awards]]\n|Best Actress In Comedy\n|A Letter From Adam\n|{{nominated}}\n|-\n|[[2015 Ghana Movie Awards]]\n|Favorite Actress\n|\n|{{nominated}}\n|-\n|}\n\n== Filmography ==\n{{Div col}}\n*''[[Things We Do for Love (Ghanaian TV series)|Thing We Do For Love]]''\n*''Divine Love ''\n*''The Heart of Men ''\n*''The Power of a Woman''\n*''Run Baby Run ''\n*''Beyonc\u00e9 - The President Daughter ''\n*''The Return of Beyonc\u00e9 ''\n*''Mummy\u2019s Daughter ''\n*''The Love Doctor ''\n*''Royal Battle ''\n*''Chasing Hope ''\n*''Princess Tyra ''\n*''the prince's bride''\n*''Fake Feelings''\n*''Wind of Love ''\n*''Total Love ''\n*''Passion of the Soul''\n*''Mortal Desire ''\n*''